message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper deals with medical image analysis using deep learning techniques, specifically for multi-organ segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MED (Medical Imaging), and cs.NEURON (Neurons and Cognition) as it involves the use of deep neural networks.
